{"tid":1454421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特別交通消息","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:30:25.000Z","uid":270234,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fbab6868944de92b13d74a161077ad330d3626a4","tid":1454421,"uid":270234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"運輸署出左特別交通消息<br />\n<br />\n交通繁忙 <br />\n暢連路、機場南交匯處、航天城交匯處、北大嶼山公路 [更新]<br />\n12/08/2019 14:45<br />\n因車多關係，下列路段的交通仍然繁忙:<br />\n-暢連路;<br />\n-機場南交匯處;<br />\n-航天城交匯處;及<br />\n-北大嶼山公路往機場方向近赤鱲角。<br />\n<br />\n市民請考慮使用非路面公共交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛人士行經上述路段敬請忍讓及小心駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家唔使block機場離境大堂，只要坐爆機鐵，再用私家車，的士入消場，遲早機場島就與世隔絕&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n一d 衝擊嘅action都唔使，就可以達到癱瘓機場嘅目標，因為佢係一個島&hellip;交通選項相當有限&hellip;"},{"pid":"7c803dd0aa9d34abe691f822d4d084cf416f1ad9","tid":1454421,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"原來咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e300d381e41e85e52ae3b5a83dbef066c5b2634","tid":1454421,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"非路面公共交通工具? <br />\n叫人搭船呀? ON99"},{"pid":"fcb2157a2613c1855d41490b10e1a14e42ec6c68","tid":1454421,"uid":80453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e300d381e41e85e52ae3b5a83dbef066c5b2634","tid":1454421,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"非路面公共交通工具? <br />\n叫人搭船呀? ON99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"乜香港境內有船搭去機場咩？<br />\n人地係咪仲停留係舊赤臘角碼頭年代？"},{"pid":"7981fbf4ae0c70b0992d58c6f96d63973a1b6315","tid":1454421,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"咩非路面, 海天碼頭又唔係對外開放, 非路面咪得機鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 